title: "🏠 DV Home"
description: "Home is where the ❤️ is"
useEqualHeights: true
statusStyle: "dot"
# Boxed group headers for stronger visual separation between sections.
headerStyle: boxed
# Let every label-discovered card surface live CPU/mem/net for its container
# (read from the docker socket). Cards without a local container (static NAS/PVE
# entries) simply have no stats to show.
showStats: true
# Homepage arranges top-level groups in a grid whose rows align to the tallest
# group, so a group with many services (Admin) stacked vertically towers over its
# short neighbours and leaves big gaps beside them. Fix: the big groups (Admin,
# Monitoring) become full-width row bands -- they span the width and wrap their
# cards instead of stacking in one tall column -- and sit at the bottom. The
# small 1-2 card groups keep the compact default grid above. Group membership is
# unchanged; only Admin/Monitoring rendering and the group order differ.
layout:
  Entertainment:
    style: row
    columns: 4
  Office:
  Media:
  Bookmarks:
  Downloaders:
  Development:
  Automation:
  Databases:
  Admin:
    style: row
    columns: 3
  Monitoring:
    style: row
    columns: 2
